author: Paige Cockburn
title: Three more deaths in NSW, one at aged care home where infected employee worked
description: The coronavirus death toll in NSW reaches 29 after a resident dies at the western Sydney aged care home where a staff member unknowingly caused an outbreak, while police condemn those who continue to flout social distancing rules.
content:
Updated 
April 18, 2020 15:58:13
Three more people in NSW have died from coronavirus including a resident at a western Sydney aged care home where a staff member unknowingly caused an outbreak.
